[The report does not state whether the outbreak strain is serotype O157 or one of the other serotypes associated with Shiga toxin production. Nor does it specifically state what differences were found between the outbreak strain and the strain isolated directly from the ground beef. Like in many bacteria infection-related foodborne illness, appropriate kitchen hygiene and adequate cooking can eliminate or at least minimize the clinical impact. - Mod.LL

The state of Vermont can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3680809,48089. Windsor County can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/vermont-county-map.gif. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
